content: Ok, so here's my assessment, either way we have to do MVP, only thing that would make sense before doing that is something either high impact manually that can drive the linkedin post, or revisiting the Dripify list to see if it's worth starting a new campaign for those that I haven't reached out to. I already DM'd all of them on the post that accepted the connection request I think. So we'd need to do an updated LinkedIn search for super high value AI influencers like Alon's level, and try to drive the post, or if you think you can give me names more effectively then we can do that.
